WEBVTT

15:24.640 --> 15:25.400 line:80%
Mother,

15:26.280 --> 15:27.310 line:80%
Changyu is in trouble.

15:27.310 --> 15:28.310 line:80%
I must go help her.

15:28.640 --> 15:31.800 line:80%
Fan Daniu is Fan Changyu's uncle.

15:32.190 --> 15:33.310 line:80%
This is essentially

15:33.310 --> 15:35.190 line:80%
an affair within the Fan family.
